I"J<p><a href="https://brxyxncorp.github.io/ultra-minimal-theme/">Ultra-Minimalista</a>
is a Jekyll theme that supports <strong>multi-page websites</strong>, and it’s not
full responsive, ‘cause was my first theme.</p>

<p>Ultra-Minimalista is useful if…</p>

<ul>
  <li>You want to create an “about me” page from a single markdown file and
host it under a custom domain name.</li>
  <li>You want to write blog from markdown file.</li>
  <li>You want something like GitHub’s <a href="http://pages.github.com/">automatic page
generator</a> for a non-code repository.</li>
</ul>
